https://developer.apple.com/library/ios/referencelibrary/GettingStarted/DevelopiOSAppsSwift/Lesson2.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40015214-CH5-SW1

run Simulator: Cmd + R
build project: Cmd + B
close Simulator: Cmd + Q

in Simulator show/hide keyboard: Cmd + K
in Simulator rotate the device: Cmd + Left or Right Arrow

status bar disappears in landscape orientation